bilingual.source: Actors often rely on cues from their fellow performers.
bilingual.target: 演员们经常依靠同伴的提示。

bilingual.source: The fellow travelers shared their stories around the campfire.
bilingual.target: 这些同伴在营火旁分享他们的故事。
与我同路旅行的人成了我的好同伴。

bilingual.source: The trail hasn't been easy for my fellow Democrats either.
bilingual.target: 这条路对我的民主党同伴来说也同样不容易。

bilingual.source: William Klein’a story may sound familiar to his fellow graduates.
bilingual.target: 威廉·克莱恩的故事在他的同伴毕业生听来很熟悉。

bilingual.source: As for Titus, he is my partner and fellow worker for you.
bilingual.target: 论到提多，他是我的同伴，一同为你们劳碌的。

bilingual.source: But I have a low threshold for some of my fellow shoppers.
bilingual.target: 但是对一些我的购物同伴来说，我的起点太低了。

bilingual.source: But they still faced discrimination and mistrust from their fellow soldiers.
bilingual.target: 但是他们仍然受到同伴的歧视和不信任。

bilingual.source: Their fellow pack members continued the attack and ultimately killed the Tenontosaurus.
bilingual.target: 它们的同伴继续攻击最终杀死了腱龙。

bilingual.source: A vampire bat comes back to his fellow vampires with a bloody mouth.
bilingual.target: 一只吸血蝙蝠带著满嘴的血回到牠的吸血同伴身边。

list.abstract: fellow（英 [ˈfeləʊ]，美 [ˈfeloʊ]），英语单词，作名词用，为男人；男孩；小伙子。作形容词用，为伙伴的；同事的；同类的。fellow短语搭配有teaching fellow（助教研究生），例句为“They often criticized their fellow scientists.（他们经常批评他们的科学家同事）”。 fellow名词类近义词有apple、customer、friend等，形容词类近义词有companionate。 fellow的复数为fellows。
Fellow是一家咖啡用具品牌公司，由Jake Miller创立。

yingyinNormal.en: We're ready. You can go in now. Surprise. For she's a jolly good fellow, For she's a jolly good fellow, For she's a jolly good fellow, And so say all of us. Hooray.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们准备好了。你现在可以进去了。惊喜！因为她是个快乐的好人，因为她是个快乐的好人，因为她是个快乐的好人，我们所有人都这样说。太棒了！

yingyinNormal.en: From a fellow space traveler. It's a true honor. The honor is mine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 作为后进的宇宙旅行者，见到你很荣幸。我也很荣幸。

yingyinNormal.en: Like that young fellow out there named Vector. He just stole a pyramid!
yingyinNormal.zh: 就像门外那个叫“向量”的年轻人，金字塔就是他偷的！

yingyinNormal.en: Is this the fellow who peed in your Hawaiian Punch? No, that was a different guy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就是那个往你的夏威夷潘趣饮料里撒尿的家伙吗？不是，那是另外一个。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey thanks. Scott Alexander, Joey Tribbianni. Joey is a fellow processor. No kidding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢了，史考，这是乔伊，乔伊他也是一个处理员。真的？

yingyinNormal.en: You are a fellow. I make the decisions here. Well, I own this hospital. You work for me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是研究员，这里我说了算。我是医院的股东，你给我打工呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, speaking as a fellow second son, I have grown rather used to being the family insult.
yingyinNormal.zh: 同样作为次子，我已经习惯了成为家族耻辱。

yingyinNormal.en: How old are you, Mr. Turing? 27. And how old were you when you became a Fellow at Cambridge? 24.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你多大了，图灵先生？呃，二十七岁。你在剑桥上学的时候多大？二十四岁。

yingyinNormal.en: Ted and his fellow California tomato growers produce close to 13 million tons of them every year.
yingyinNormal.zh: 泰德和其他的加州番茄种植者每年能收获将近一千三百万吨番茄。

yingyinNormal.en: Blood it ran down through this fellow's face and eyes. It was when that he go in and called for medic.
yingyinNormal.zh: 血顺着这家伙的脸跟眼流下，那是当他开始呼喊军医的时候。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you so much. Thank you. Mr. Speaker, Mr. Vice President, members of Congress, my fellow Americans.
yingyinNormal.zh: 非常感谢。谢谢，议长先生，副总统先生。各位国会议员，我的美国同胞们。

yingyinNormal.en: And when this 13-year old man was asked about his fellow amputees, he said this: First, they will be sad.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当问到这位13岁的小伙子对其他截肢患者们的想法时，他说道 “起初，他们会感到悲痛。”

yingyinNormal.en: Well, my fellow Americans, before this year is out, we will put a Wolowitz on one of America's top models.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我亲爱的美国兄弟们，不出今年我们就可以把沃罗威茨送到一个超级模特身边去。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, by the way, a fellow at work said I could use his Dodger tickets this weekend. Does that sound like fun?
yingyinNormal.zh: 对了，我一个同事说要给我周末道奇队比赛的门票，应该很好玩吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. You know, I have always been intrigued by flip-flops. The official footwear of the laid-back fellow. Okay, sure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我倒是一直对人字拖感到好奇。悠闲之人的标配鞋。你高兴就好。

yingyinNormal.en: I read recently about a fellow in Kansas with an enormous ball of twine. I bet you could give him a run for his money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我最近得知堪萨斯州一个家伙拿麻绳团了一个巨大的球，我认为你可以跟他一比高下。

yingyinNormal.en: Describing how you came to be on school property after hours, using alcohol and drugs, where a fellow student almost died.
yingyinNormal.zh: 描述一下，为什么放学之后你们会在学校喝酒，吸大麻，还差点害死一个学生。

yingyinNormal.en: My fellow Americans, we know how to do this. We've done it before. It's the way we used to do business and we can do it that way again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的同胞们，我们都知道如何做到这些。我们以前曾做到过。这是我们曾经走过的路，让我们再走一遍。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, that's right. And, so far, each of your fellow defendants has specifically denied being part of that process. Now, I'm going to ask you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，没错。到现在为止，其他几位被告都否认自己曾参与这一过程。现在，我要问你。

yingyinNormal.en: Of course he's got a name. He's mine. I bought him off an Irishman fellow I met at a pub last year. I lent him to Dumbledore to guard the...Yes?
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然有名字，他是我的是我去年在酒馆向一个爱尔兰人买的，后来借给邓布利多去看守...什么？

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们让芝加哥的火车通勤者与他们的同伴交谈。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 2009年，美国公共部门的工会成员数量超过了私营部门的同伴。
